<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="20Dec1938"><font color="red">20 December 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on): &hellip; title &hellip; secret &hellip; reasons[?] &hellip; I have just received your letter of December 18th &hellip; I have noted Mr Joyce&apos;s wishes about the title-page and about the binding for the book and its jacket &hellip; He shall have proofs of the preliminary pages shortly, and I shall be sending him specimens for the binding early in the New Year. </div>
